00:15:17.640 --> 00:15:18.960
They're wide open...

00:15:19.740 --> 00:15:22.680
but if I kill them now, it'll just complicate my escape.

00:15:29.680 --> 00:15:31.030
Good job today.

00:15:37.880 --> 00:15:41.920
Let me know once you've rested a bit, and I'll check your vitals.

00:15:44.300 --> 00:15:47.250
Again with the dorky shirts, Yukimura-san?

00:15:47.250 --> 00:15:48.990
N-Not this one, too?!

00:15:48.990 --> 00:15:52.220
I thought it'd be a breath of fresh air in your solitary lifestyle!

00:15:52.220 --> 00:15:54.090
To be honest, it ticks me off.

00:15:54.090 --> 00:15:56.810
And I like this brand, too.

00:15:56.810 --> 00:16:00.060
Well, they don't go over well with my students, either.

00:16:00.680 --> 00:16:01.660
Students?

00:16:01.660 --> 00:16:03.020
Aguri!

00:16:03.020 --> 00:16:05.650
Just how long does a simple data check take?!

00:16:05.650 --> 00:16:07.320
I-I'm sorry, Koutarou-sa—

00:16:09.990 --> 00:16:15.450
I'm only marrying you out of pity, since your father's one of our subcontractors!

00:16:15.450 --> 00:16:17.420
Now, repay that kindness!

00:16:17.420 --> 00:16:21.080
Follow my orders with utmost effort and whole-hearted devotion!

00:16:23.010 --> 00:16:25.130
And as for you, my guinea pig...

00:16:26.740 --> 00:16:28.300
See you tomorrow.

00:16:34.290 --> 00:16:38.200
Generating antimatter within life forms:

00:16:38.200 --> 00:16:40.810
That was the core of Yanagisawa's research.

00:16:42.390 --> 00:16:48.380
He sought to incorporate antimatter-generating particle acceleration cycles into biomolecular networks

00:16:48.380 --> 00:16:52.280
and activate the intracellular machinery through colossal energy.

00:16:53.150 --> 00:16:54.330
Yanagisawa?

00:16:54.330 --> 00:16:55.200
Hmm?

00:16:55.200 --> 00:16:57.620
My hands and feet are pretty numb.

00:16:58.040 --> 00:16:59.610
And I'm getting chills.

00:17:00.080 --> 00:17:02.140
That's Yanagisawa-san to you!

00:17:02.140 --> 00:17:05.510
Tch. Peripheral neuropathy, eh?

00:17:06.040 --> 00:17:08.730
Perhaps we should stop administering the alkaloid?

00:17:08.730 --> 00:17:13.950
Yeah. If it starts affecting polymerization of macromolecules, this'll all be for nothing.

00:17:08.730 --> 00:17:12.220
If I can skillfully manipulate the experiment myself,

00:17:12.220 --> 00:17:14.650
I can boost the probability of success even further.

00:17:16.520 --> 00:17:19.780
I'll gain powers of destruction beyond all human reckoning.

00:17:23.480 --> 00:17:26.690
Wow, so much on my checklist today!

00:17:26.690 --> 00:17:29.800
Better hurry it along or I'll get smacked around again.

00:17:29.800 --> 00:17:31.950
And I guess you don't want that, huh?

00:17:31.950 --> 00:17:33.400
Yeah, basically.

00:17:33.400 --> 00:17:37.860
I'm actually a teacher, so I can't be getting stupid, now.

00:17:38.280 --> 00:17:39.210
A teacher?

00:17:39.210 --> 00:17:40.480
Aguri!

00:17:40.480 --> 00:17:42.600
How many times do I have to tell you? Don't keep me waiting!

00:17:42.600 --> 00:17:44.250
I'm sorry! I'll do it right now!

00:17:44.250 --> 00:17:47.240
Your physical ability and clerical skills are all you're good for!

00:17:47.240 --> 00:17:49.920
Can't you observe one lousy guinea pig?!

00:17:50.520 --> 00:17:52.420
Maybe I'll have to beat it into—

00:18:01.480 --> 00:18:04.140
Mr. Reaper... What did you do?

00:18:04.140 --> 00:18:05.930
I've immobilized him. That's all.

00:18:06.560 --> 00:18:09.610
Now you can still teach tomorrow, right?

00:18:12.390 --> 00:18:15.440
After he had spent about three months in this place,

00:18:15.440 --> 00:18:19.340
the killer and the teacher were as open with each other as old friends.

00:18:21.670 --> 00:18:23.500
Quadratic equations?

00:18:23.500 --> 00:18:26.060
You have to dress it up a little more, or it'll feel too easy.

00:18:26.580 --> 00:18:30.000
That goes double for students at a college-prep school.

00:18:26.580 --> 00:18:34.550
The equation x² - kx + (3√3 - 9)/2 = 0, which is quadratic in x, has two roots, and their difference is (5√3 - 2)/2. Find the value of k.

00:18:30.000 --> 00:18:34.550
Urgh... The professional teacher, being schooled by an assassin...

00:18:35.130 --> 00:18:38.380
You're better suited to be a teacher than I am, Mr. Reaper.

00:18:38.380 --> 00:18:42.150
Well, I can play a college professor if work demands it.

00:18:42.800 --> 00:18:45.850
But I'm not cut out for teaching.

00:18:46.880 --> 00:18:51.340
I had a pupil once... but he betrayed me.

00:18:52.660 --> 00:18:55.210
That's how I wound up here.

00:18:58.740 --> 00:19:02.940
Now the Reaper's name and all his skills are mine alone.

00:19:03.510 --> 00:19:04.790
And that's not all.

00:19:05.370 --> 00:19:09.050
I recently mastered a disguise technique that even you don't have.

00:19:10.320 --> 00:19:12.540
Farewell, my teacher.

00:19:12.540 --> 00:19:15.800
You never did see my face, did you?

00:19:16.980 --> 00:19:18.980
I still don't understand.

00:19:18.980 --> 00:19:23.960
I had developed his abilities and supervised him almost perfectly, and yet...

00:19:26.440 --> 00:19:28.270
I think I get it.

00:19:29.110 --> 00:19:34.190
Your student probably just wanted to be seen. By you.

00:19:35.160 --> 00:19:37.150
But I did see him.

00:19:37.650 --> 00:19:42.100
Closely observing someone's abilities and personality is key to winning them over.

00:19:46.280 --> 00:19:49.560
Break time's over, guinea pig.

00:19:49.560 --> 00:19:53.220
Get back on the restraint table. We're doing more testing.

00:19:54.920 --> 00:19:58.040
The subject's body is starting to undergo strange changes.

00:19:58.550 --> 00:20:02.220
Given the enormous energy within, if he were to rebel...

00:20:02.220 --> 00:20:06.560
If he's planning on making a run for it, he'll take Aguri hostage.

00:20:06.560 --> 00:20:07.180
Huh?

00:20:07.180 --> 00:20:12.170
She's a docile and reasonably capable specimen whose death no one would mourn.

00:20:12.890 --> 00:20:17.930
In other words, a canary to gauge his malice.

00:20:25.530 --> 00:20:28.120
Rejection response is within expectations.

00:20:28.120 --> 00:20:30.170
You may leave him be.

00:20:39.840 --> 00:20:42.280
She was to be a living sacrifice.

00:20:43.480 --> 00:20:47.040
The Reaper was turning into something that wasn't human.

00:20:48.160 --> 00:20:50.100
And though she sensed these things...

00:20:50.100 --> 00:20:53.060
she was not the type to ask unnecessary questions.

00:21:00.400 --> 00:21:02.530
Good job again today.

00:21:02.530 --> 00:21:05.660
Once you've rested a bit, I'll check your vitals.

00:21:06.840 --> 00:21:09.300
Then we can talk, like always.

00:21:10.670 --> 00:21:15.400
She just looks straight ahead and smiles peacefully. Like always.

00:21:17.290 --> 00:21:22.400
Oh... So this is what "seeing" is.

00:21:23.920 --> 00:21:25.130
Yes, let's.

00:21:25.450 --> 00:21:37.350
komorebi ga yasashiku sashikomu ookina mado no naka
As the dappled sunlight shone gently through the window

00:21:25.760 --> 00:21:27.500
How are those exam questions coming?

00:21:28.180 --> 00:21:31.500
The legendary killer who'd never shown himself to anyone

00:21:31.890 --> 00:21:35.820
knew for the first time the happiness in being seen.
I-I'd like your opinion on a few of them.

00:21:37.350 --> 00:21:47.610
kimi to deatta ano hi wo tooku ni kanjita
The day I met you felt so far away

00:21:40.550 --> 00:21:42.820
The seasons changed yet again.

00:21:42.820 --> 00:21:49.780
Her new batch of students met as Class 3-E of Kunugigaoka Junior High...

00:21:49.260 --> 00:21:58.850
sukoshi zutsu narabeta omoi ga boku wo atatameru
The memories I've arranged little by little keep me warm

00:21:51.720 --> 00:21:57.960
two weeks before the crescent moon came to be.

00:21:59.920 --> 00:21:59.920


00:22:00.240 --> 00:22:11.870
chiisana heya tsunagu kokoro sotto oshiete kureta
A small room, hearts connecting: you taught me gently

00:22:11.870 --> 00:22:24.660
kono kisetsu ga mukae ni kitara kimi no sugata mou sagasu koto mo
Once this season comes for me, I won't be able

00:22:24.660 --> 00:22:29.900
dekinaku nacchaun da ne dekinaku nacchaun da ne
To seek you out anymore, will I?

00:22:29.900 --> 00:22:35.540
zutto wasurezu ni iru yo zutto wasurezu ni iru yo
But I'll hold your memory in my heart

00:22:35.540 --> 00:22:41.520
mata kimi ni aeru hi made mata kimi ni aeru hi made
Until the day I can see you again